title: How to get S rank on Nami?

embed.description: Every game is a story; visit the new League of Legends match history to check out how this one ends and share your own!

body: How does a 4/4/6 Vayne with average-ish farm get a S- rank and their Nami support with a 1/0/17 only get an A+? This makes no sense at all, I warded the most, didn't die, had 3 turret last hits and even did more damage to enemy champs than our Zed but can't get an S. Frustrating as hell how hard it is to get the last S I need to finish off my Nami mastery, surely the average Nami player isn't out there farming it up?

replies.body:
LOL, i got less kda overall and was getting S+, feelsbadman

Hit level 7 within 4 games (1 was a loss)
lmao, try full AP nami in ARAM and see how easy it is to get an S.
The average nami, due to being a support, doesn't have her grade get affected by CS
